   <body>
      <p>The <uicontrol>Workflow Action Complete</uicontrol> event enables you to execute the logic once you perform a workflow action. You can use this event  to execute  a logic  on clicking the workflow action. </p>
      <section product="Include_PG_Content">
         <title>Use Case # Insert a new record on performing a workflow action such as Submit</title>
         <p>In the   RFP form, once you perform the workflow action <uicontrol>Submit</uicontrol> for the  <uicontrol>Create Change Order</uicontrol> page, it creates a new record in the <uicontrol>Change Order</uicontrol> form for the same contract.</p>
